comments: Davis (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Tate (HOU) and absorbs the contact.
Tate (HOU) makes marginal contact to Davis' (LAL) arm during his drive that doesn't affect his SBQR.
Bazemore (LAL) and Wood (HOU) mutually engage and disengage during the screen.
Westbrook (LAL) makes marginal contact to Green's (HOU) body on the perimeter.
Tate (HOU) has his forearm resting on James' (LAL) back and makes marginal contact as he spins away from the contact.
Wood (HOU) dislodges Davis (LAL) from his position during the rebound.
Wood (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Bradley (LAL) and makes marginal contact to his body.
Bazemore (LAL) makes contact to Wood's (HOU) arm that affects his SBQR.  The contact occurs prior to his upward shooting motion.
